'''''Fu'ulanh''''' was a vessel used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. It was intended to transport members of the [[Shaper caste]] and the [[Order of Yun-Yuuzhan]] to [[Borleias/Legends|Borleias]], with the intent of turning the world into haven for the [[Priest/Legends|Priests]] of [[Yun-Yuuzhan]]. However, [[Warmaster]] [[Tsavong Lah]] actually intended it to be the place of death for [[Priest/Legends|Priest]] [[Takhaff Uul]] and [[Master Shaper]] [[Ghithra Dal]], who had sabotaged the Warmaster's [[radank]] claw-arm, and those who had aided them. Lah fed the thirty conspirators to four [[Rancor/Legends|rancors]] that had been hidden aboard the ''Fu'ulanh'', but would inform the Shaper and [[Priest caste]]s that the vessel was destroyed by [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] fighters upon reaching Borleias. The ''Fu'ulanh'' was presumably destroyed sometime after that.

